---
title: Mediterranean-Style Beef & Pork Bowl with Spinach Couscous & Almonds
description: How satisfying is saucy beef and pork mince on a bed of fluffy couscous? You'll have to make this delectable Mediterranean-inspired dish to find out! As a nice surprise, we've added almonds plus a cooling yoghurt to top it off. Simply delicious.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
